results.description: Open since 1990 and brimming with energy and nostalgia, The St. Paul Grill is a destination unto itself. Located in the historic Saint Paul Hotel and overlooking Rice Park, the iconic restaurant is known for its refined style, attentive service, and exceptional cuisine. Our culinary team prepares American steakhouse classics with unparalleled quality and attention-to-detail. Our bar program boasts an impressive selection of rare spirits, an award-winning wine list, and a collection of classic cocktails. Our team of passionate bartenders, servers, and hospitality professionals are intuitive, enthusiastic, and always authentically themselves.
